    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_3",
    "text": "FAMILY Harry, Holly, Emma and Steve",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.05175601243244797,
      0.17286706354040257,
      0.21996303058973304,
      0.181795634968974
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_4",
    "text": "EXCLUSIVE",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.04617056297545652,
      0.18878755921874082,
      0.14236917984565073,
      0.20365430109549454
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_5",
    "text": "BY MATTHEW BARBOUR",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.048059154733859466,
      0.20634920656478611,
      0.16081330743496355,
      0.21511627873528588
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_6",
    "text": "A t the age of four, while her little pals were running about, laughing and giggling, Emma Griffin remembers \"playing with dead people\".",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.04805915048691148,
      0.22093023371843448,
      0.19963031298025008,
      0.2892441857867058
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_7",
    "text": "Another childhood memory is of Sunday afternoons, when other mums and dads were out for a stroll after lunch and her parents, Pat and Pip, would be holding a seance to commune with the other side.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.04805914833352479,
      0.28918650793774625,
      0.16451016386610562,
      0.38665674597462807
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_25",
    "text": "The modern Molly Weasley who is using chat brooms to work magic",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.7519175522254175,
      0.3385416663191054,
      0.9541822645861726,
      0.5316343515592934
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 12
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_8",
    "text": "Emma, 48, now a fulltime witch, says: \"It seemed normal for me to see - and play with dead people from the age of just four.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.04805915029328594,
      0.38808139556219473,
      0.1700554534035717,
      0.44622092987385187
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 13
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_9",
    "text": "\"My first time was at Hampton Court, but ever since then, it's happened regularly. My younger brother Ben and I knew our parents were different, but then, aren't evervone's?\"",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.04805914982416401,
      0.4461805556236747,
      0.18302503408173082,
      0.5236200916378334
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 14
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_10",
    "text": "She says she inherited her mum's magical powers and \"came out of the closet - the broom closet\" after her parents died from cancer in 2019 and 2020.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.04805915014203001,
      0.5260416667040044,
      0.21811460481509135,
      0.5741567459140662
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 15
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_35",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "picture",
    "bbox": [
      0.7619781699507907,
      0.5381600839120371,
      0.9629982922204464,
      0.7778273809523809
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 16
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_11",
    "text": "he is now a full-time witch, cine reading\". She says: \"I'm the real-life Molly Weasley. Everyone calls me that.\"",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.048059147393069754,
      0.5857558141910705,
      0.20887245809815427,
      0.6528571348523083
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 17
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_12",
    "text": "But, unlike the Harry Potter witch, she is a thoroughly modern Molly, with 96,000 followers on Instagram and 40,000 on TikTok.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.04795693578040092,
      0.6540178571213549,
      0.16266173886149257,
      0.722790142622682
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 18
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_13",
    "text": "And she recently cast her spell on 262 would-be magic makers from across the world, initiating them as witches in one big, free Zoom session.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.048059147482820926,
      0.723837209661032,
      0.1682070227465343,
      0.7921626984242
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 19
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_27",
    "text": "has always been open with her kids about being a witch. She says: \"They were attracted to the spirituality of it",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.7781885439977277,
      0.7906746032669472,
      0.9556377096067085,
      0.8183139532769439
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 20
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_26",
    "text": "Talking of the Zoom witch initiation, which included women from as far away as Finland and Australia, she says: \"I guided them through the ceremony, helping them become witches, telling them to spread the word far and wide.\"",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5970425138338734,
      0.7921511629424927,
      0.7726432576541119,
      0.8591269839686327
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 21
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_14",
    "text": "Emma did not discover her mum was a witch until she was 17, when she rushed home in tears after visiting a psychic fair with Steve, now her husband.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.04805915160453235,
      0.7921511630282799,
      0.16451016774780605,
      0.8591269842236623
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 22
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_16",
    "text": "It seemed normal to me to see dead people",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.17740621308838941,
      0.8123290684301613,
      0.26067142258723114,
      0.8866279065123597
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 23
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_29",
    "text": "Her husband is also on \"team witch\", says Emma, whose website has attracted clients wanting help with everything from mental health to fertility issues.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.7781885442171851,
      0.818313953494818,
      0.9537892774053878,
      0.8692956350244805
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 24
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_23",
    "text": "Emma says: \"When I tell people I'm a witch, the majority are fascinated and love hearing about what I do, from helping people find happiness to healing them, even helping them conceive, like I myself did 25 years ago.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.41200912428676534,
      0.8313492061997444,
      0.5452865033457335,
      0.9593023252469138
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 25
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_20",
    "text": "daughter Holly, then son Harry three years later.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.28271242883944037,
      0.8514659026066159,
      0.40665434443491594,
      0.8826053926293074
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 26
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_28",
    "text": "She has faced hostility from people saying she will \"go to hell for working for the devil\", but Emma says being a witch is \"positive and natural\". And she",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6857350991461666,
      0.8603670635404024,
      0.7726752508060147,
      0.9578488368637091
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 27
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_15",
    "text": "A tarot reader had told her she and Steve, then also 17 and an art student like her, would never have children.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.048059149654456214,
      0.8603670636726383,
      0.16266173711387408,
      0.9084821429133154
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 28
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_36",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "picture",
    "bbox": [
      0.6152294461852288,
      0.8618887442129629,
      0.6849455048333053,
      0.939820240162037
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 29
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_31",
    "text": "She says: \"I intend to keep spreading the word. Those muggles (people without magical talents) are really missing out.\"",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.7800369724298953,
      0.8675515811435074,
      0.9540179114635434,
      0.9084821427888026
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 30
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_21",
    "text": "Soon after, moving from London to Cornwall to be closer to nature, Emma began giving",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.2846428115395406,
      0.8807043649220143,
      0.40665434353296165,
      0.9201388888197483
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 31
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_17",
    "text": "EMMA GRIFFIN WITCH ON PARANORMAL POWER",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.17929759706398551,
      0.8908730159586927,
      0.2735674644886947,
      0.9069940476587184
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 32
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_30",
    "text": "·Follow Emma at instagram.com/ emmagriffinwitch. Her book, The Witch's Way Home, is out now",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.7800369695601082,
      0.908430232892621,
      0.9537892763425412,
      0.9374999997694745
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 33
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_18",
    "text": "Determined to help, her mum confessed she was actually a sorceress and would teach Emma the skills to prove the reader wrong. In 1999, Emma and Steve had",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.059149723338137714,
      0.909883720979072,
      0.1626617382145425,
      0.9201388888607197
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 34
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_19",
    "text": "clients spiritual guidance, while working in jobs ranging from fashion design to illustration.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.23105360656448307,
      0.920058139638229,
      0.4066543416795096,
      0.9491567458050546
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 35
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_32",
    "text": "features@mirror.co.uk X@DailyMirror",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.8632162640235888,
      0.9389534886042852,
      0.9537892782540396,
      0.9549418602510927
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
    "order": 36
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_22",
    "text": "She became a full-time witch around five years ago and initiated nursery manager Holly as a sea witch in 2021, making a third generation of witches in her family.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.24214418299636878,
      0.9491279069831902,
      0.40665433832217707,
      0.9593253969638573
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029",
